stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> DragRecognition: Mouse down on draggable
    DragRecognition --> Idle: Mouse up (click)
    DragRecognition --> Dragging: Movement exceeds threshold
    Dragging --> DragOver: Cursor enters drop target
    DragOver --> Dragging: Cursor leaves drop target
    DragOver --> Dropped: Mouse up on valid target
    Dragging --> Cancelled: Mouse up outside targets
    Dropped --> Idle: Drop handled
    Cancelled --> Idle: Cancel handled
